<p>From importing over 1/2 Million establishments to my DB, to fixing some of the data issues, it has been a really fun learning practice.</p>

<p><em>But what did I build? What is the API for?</em></p>

<p>Basically, I re-wrote the <a href="https://api.ratings.food.gov.uk/help" target="_blank">FHRS API</a>! Lets take a quick peek shall we ­¤śü</p>

<p>This is the establishment query. This will lookup an establishment based on itŌĆÖs FHRS_ID - I havenŌĆÖt given them my own IDŌĆÖsŌĆ” yet ­¤śē</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>{
